      "title": "Power cuts are reduced to one hour on weekends",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Public Utilities Commission has issued an announcement regarding the manner in which electricity cuts will be carried out from September 03 to 05. Accordingly, there will be a one-hour power cut during that weekend. On Monday, there will be a two-hour power cut. Power cuts are made at night during weekends and power cuts are made for one hour during the day and one hour during the night on Mondays."
      ],
